Name: Joggernauts
About the game: Switch places at just the right time to beat color-coded levels. Work together as a team. No jogger left behind! Co-op that’s actually cooperative. You Jump for Two! You Switch for Two! You Coordinate the Two! Your cat watches. (Cat not included) It’s like patting your head and rubbing your belly, but you’re jogging. Only 2 buttons! How hard can that be? Difficulty modifiers to play faster, slower, safer, or danger...er. Mind-bending action puzzles that hate you. There is one! With a robot. And a ton of really great music! It’s got a Funny Funny Joke (Limit 1). And super secret secrets to find! And trophies to collect. … in space.
